{
  "id": "adv_event_2406_02_05",
  "title": "ⅢX_お礼はkanaまで.mov",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ラスベガスではお互いにいろいろ大変でしたけど……\nまあ……お世話になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We both had a lot of trouble in Las Vegas…\nWell… thank you for taking care of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.1985035895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "あれから少しだけ英語の勉強始めてみたんです\n本気で海外進出狙うならやっとかなきゃなーって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I started studying English a little bit after that.\nI figured I had to do it if I was serious about expanding overseas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3985034942,
      "endTime": 16.3048753738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.5182087262
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "きっとこれから海外の仕事も増えてくるだろうし……\nえ？　増えますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure we’ll be getting more jobs overseas…\nRight? They will increase‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.5182087262,
      "endTime": 22.272517236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.4791836738
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "そのたびにあのガキにからかわれるのもウザいですし\n自分で交渉とかもいろいろ出来るようになりたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s annoying getting teased by that brat every time‚\nand I want to be able to negotiate and do various things on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4791836738,
      "endTime": 29.6912472724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも今後、ⅢXが海外進出\nするためにもう少し勉強しておいて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ you should also study a little more so that IIIX can expand overseas\nin the future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8779140154,
      "endTime": 36.4963267963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.7029934247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "ところでギャラの取り分に関してなんですけど\nもう少しこちらの割合増やせませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ regarding the division of the fee…\nCan’t you increase our share a bit more?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7029934247,
      "endTime": 42.7629936536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "ⅢXが加入したことで星見プロの財源も\n潤ってきたことでしょうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hoshimi Pro’s finances must be flourishing\nnow that IIIX has joined.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9696602822,
      "endTime": 48.1867578507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.3867580414
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "もう少し還元してくれてもいいと思うんですよね\nこの機会だから言わせてもらうんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think you could give us a little more back.\nI’m gonna take this opportunity to say this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.3867580414,
      "endTime": 54.709887504600005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.923220857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "ケータリングに関しても前々から思ってるとこがあって\nあ、え、待って、スマホの充電切れそ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve also had some thoughts about the catering for a while now.\nAh‚ eh‚ wait‚ my phone’s about to die――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.923220857,
      "endTime": 61.1884591421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ryokan-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.5884082476
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です\n{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work.\n{user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6995692889,
      "endTime": 65.0355104129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "あくまで契約上の付き合いなのに、わざわざ動画を\n撮って感謝を伝えるだなんて、おかしな気もしますが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a bit strange to go out of your way to make a video and express gratitude\nwhen it’s just a business relationship‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.2329026222,
      "endTime": 72.20038547509999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ryokan-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.3995692889
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "一応、私も参加させていただきました\n角が立つと面倒ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but I participated anyway.\nIt’s troublesome if things get messy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3995692889,
      "endTime": 78.68297058739999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ryokan-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.8995692889
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね、ラスベガスでライブをした時は\nお世話になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ thank you for taking care of us\nwhen we had the live in Las Vegas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8995692889,
      "endTime": 84.0136056582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "海外公演は久々でしたし、いい経験になりました\n一筋縄ではいかないことも多かったですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It had been a while since we had an overseas performance‚ so it was a good experience.\nAlthough there were a lot of things that weren’t easy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1995692889,
      "endTime": 92.02791392009999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ryokan-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.2329026222
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "franとkanaを、貴方に押し付け……いえ\n貴方が見てくれていたおかげで、多少は楽が出来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You took fran and kana off my hands… No‚\nthanks to you looking after them‚ things have gotten a little easier for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.2329026222,
      "endTime": 101.2768706321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事の後に、軽く街を見て回ったんですが\nたまには観光もいいものですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I took a quick look around the town after work‚\nand sightseeing isn’t so bad once in a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.4662359556,
      "endTime": 107.4586397489,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ryokan-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.4662359556
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、今日みたいに地方のお仕事ばかりというのも\n考えものではありますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ having nothing but local jobs like today\nis something to think about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6662359556,
      "endTime": 113.2687981924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "プレタポルテから移籍した直後\nお仕事の減っていた時期から懇意にしていたとはいえ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right after transferring from Pret-A-Porter…\nEven though we’ve been on good terms since the time when we had fewer jobs…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.4662359556,
      "endTime": 119.52090705239999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ryokan-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.4662359556
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "また地方の健康ランドに出向くはめになるなんて……\nソロで受けれた分、うるさいのがいないのはいいですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To think we’d end up going to a local health land again…\nAt least when I got solo jobs‚ there were no noisy brats around.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.7329026222,
      "endTime": 128.0550116539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、これからもfranと\nkanaのこと、よろしくお願いしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ from now on too‚ please take care of\nfran and kana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.2662359556,
      "endTime": 133.6991385778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ryokan-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.2662359556
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.0083480199
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kan-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さーん、いつもkanaのために\n汗水垂らして働いてくれてありがと～っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san～! Thanks for always working so hard for kana!\nThanks for working your butt off!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.9991439184,
      "endTime": 143.4197107633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.6324772517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kan-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "これからも馬車馬のごとく働いてどんどんkanaに\n大きな仕事を持ってきてね～！　よろしくっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From now on too‚ work like a horse and keep bringing kana bigger and bigger jobs～!\nTake care～!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.6324772517,
      "endTime": 151.7199828783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kan-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "kanaの人気が爆上がりするような仕事がいいな～\n海外の仕事とか～有名な映像作品の主演とか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want jobs that’ll make kana’s popularity explode～!\nLike jobs overseas～ or starring in a famous film!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.9324772517,
      "endTime": 161.7469893138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.9324772517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
